Local Dev Run:
Frontend Init:
- cd frontend // move to frontend folder 
- npm install // install the required modules
- npm run dev // run the React App as frontend

Backend Init:
- .\apmsvenv\Scripts\activate // enable virtual environment
- pip install -r requirements.txt // install the required modules
- alembic upgrade head // run the migrations
- uvicorn backend.main:app --reload // run the FastAPI app as backend

